ASK
That saying, “be careful what you ask for”... all wrong. Don’t be careful what you ask for. ASK AND ASK AWAY TO YOUR HEARTS CONTENT! Ask often, ask truthfully, ask without maliciousness, ask with good intention, ask with all the belief in your heart that what you ask for is possible. Most importantly ASK IN GREAT DETAIL! Imagine it, go over and over it again in your mind until your body can FEEL IT. Smile because it’s coming! And when it shows up, you better PAY ATTENTION, LISTEN and ALLOW because you have manifested it and the universe has gifted it to you. ❤️Te amo amor. ➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖

WHO?
Have you ever stopped to wonder how all these rules came about? How things became structured the way they are? WHO decided money would be better than trade? That some would get more and some less? The smart fucker that thought up taxes and forced us all to pay, or manipulated it’s way or maybe FEAR so effortlessly came to play? That some lives would be seen as more precious than others? That land would be divided and owned? WHO made up these silly little BIG rules as to WHO could cross these imaginary borders that Mother Earth intended to keep open and free? WHO made up the bullshit bureaucracy that grants us PERMISSION to live in these man made zones and work to support our loved ones? WHO decides what’s “cool” or what’s not? What’s in the season or what’s out? What’s rude or polite? What's pretty or “ugly”? What’s right or wrong? Who’s crazy or sane, short or tall, fat or skinny, rich or poor, able or not, wise or stupid? WHO decided science is more credible than psychic/healing/spiritual energy? That doctors are more valuable than artists? That one needs validation through a certificate or diploma to be considered “knowledgeable”? WHO created court systems that only grants freedom to those with enough money to buy their freedom? WHO designed governments that only work for the rich to get richer and made up voting systems that often feel like a game given to a child to keep them busy while the real shit goes down? WHO made up all these silly little BIG rules, labels and blah blah blahs that continue to divide, instill fear, doubt and shame us? WHO chose to give them attention, credibility and power? WHO followed the imaginary leader when we were all leaders to begin with? WHO chose the top “WHO” anyways? I know WHO... the fearful ones.
Be your own person. Fuck labels. Division is an illusion. One love. BeYOUtiful. ➖ photo by @sandraaerialist #movMEANT ➖ movMEANT.com
